{"type":"message","id":"eea29c5b","parentId":"cfa5c4f5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:11:29.817Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Run your Session Startup sequence - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, April 13th, 2026 - 8:11 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-13 12:11 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776082289810}}
{"type":"message","id":"3dc206d9","parentId":"eea29c5b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:11:37.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me follow the Session Startup sequence from AGENTS.md:\n\n1. Read `SOUL.md` — already in context\n2. Read `USER.md` — already in context\n3. Read `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` (today + yesterday) — today is 2026-04-13, yesterday is 2026-04-12\n4. If in MAIN SESSION: Also read `MEMORY.md` — already in context\n5. Read session context from `~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json`\n6. Read most recent session summary\n\nLet me check the memory files and session context.","thinkingSignature":"6ad8fb2de7974337f527d83deef5f4558f8b42d56843c7799b2c0051bea62130"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n0c2m1frlzfn_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/2026-04-13.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n0c2m1frlzfn_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main/memory/2026-04-12.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n0c2m1frlzfn_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/sessions/main@*/context.json 2>/dev/null | head -1 | xargs cat 2>/dev/null"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_n0c2m1frlzfn_4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t ~/.openclaw/sessions/*/session-summary.md 2>/dev/null | head -1 | xargs cat 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":311,"cacheRead":7794,"cacheWrite":11613,"totalTokens":19772,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00037319999999999996,"cacheRead":0.00046763999999999996,"cacheWrite":0.004354875,"total":0.005211915}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776082289823,"responseId":"062c1070773a4ddcbee435393284b818"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ac0d09a7","parentId":"3dc206d9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:11:37.422Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_n0c2m1frlzfn_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-13 日志\n\n## 14:39-14:52 主要讨论\n\n### 技能检查\n- 已安装 26 个 workspace 技能 + ~58 个系统内置技能\n- 无实质性冲突，openclaw-router 是唯一多余组件（半成品）\n\n### 记忆链路分析\n- ephemeral 有数据（Apr 13 04:45-05:05 UTC，5条）\n- session-summary 从未验证过完整链路\n- MEMORY.md 之前写入失败（文件不存在）\n\n### 框架状态\n- 3108 scene-classifier: 手动抢的 8091 端口，可能漂移\n- 3103 scorer: ✅ 在线，text/prompt 兼容已修复\n- cron: wiki-auto-learn 每小时，memory-keeper 每天4点，memory-maintain 每天3点\n\n### 结论\n- task_orchestrator 是实际在跑的任务编排逻辑\n- 真正缺的是完整 /new 测试验证记忆链路\n- 已在 MEMORY.md 写入强制启动规则和关键状态\n\n### 15:22-15:25 框架检查 + scene-classifier 修复\n\n#### 框架状态\n- 3103 scorer: ✅ 正常（port 3103）\n- 3105 scene-classifier v2: ✅ 刚修复 numpy.float32 bug（之前500错误）\n- 3104: ❌ 废弃，被3105替代\n- openclaw-router: ⚠️ 仍在跑（pid 434），但 MEMORY 标记为半成品\n- cron: memory-maintain/memory-keeper 正常，wiki-auto-learn 未找到\n\n#### numpy.float32 bug 修复\n- 位置：`v8/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py` + `workspace/skills/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py`\n- 问题：`top_conf`、`w`、`gap` 未转 Python float，FastAPI jsonable_encoder 报错\n- 修复：`top_conf = float(weights[0])`、`float(w)`、`float(weights[0]-weights[1])`\n- 重启：kill 66439 → nohup python3 api_server.py\n\n#### 记忆链路\n- ephemeral → session-summary: ✅\n- session-summary → bootstrap: ❌ 仍断（事件在首条回复后才触发）\n\n### 待做\n- [ ] 修复 bootstrap-context 时序\n- [ ] 确认 wiki-auto-learn 是否存在\n- [ ] 决定 openclaw-router 去留\n\n\n## 19:00-19:54 系统性评审+修复（5轮）\n\n### 本次完成的工作\n\n**核心修复**\n- `auto-score-classify` HOOK.md 端口 3104→3105（旧端口已废弃）\n- `session-summary/handler.js` JSDoc `@returns` 类型修正\n- `wiki-learn-once.sh` blocklist 精确匹配（有子串误匹配bug）\n- `session-summary` 新增 `pruneOldSummaries(30天)` 防文件堆积\n- `ephemeral isMeaningful` 放宽（先放宽后回退 `duration>=2` 条件）\n\n**端口链路（最终确认）**\n```\ngateway → auto-score-classify → 3105/scene-classifier\n                     ↓\n              3103/scorer (风险评分)\n                     ↓\n              session-summary hook\n```\n\n**entities 最终状态**\n- 目标：28（触发线31）\n- 当前：31（稳定）\n- blocklist：15个唯一条目\n- auto-ingested：20个，其余为手动创建\n\n**3101 context-api（openclaw-router）**\n- 确认为 systemd 服务（openclaw-router.service + openclaw-context.service）\n- 已停止并禁用，3101端口释放\n- 之前杀进程自动重启，需 `systemctl disable` 才能彻底移除\n\n**Wiki-learn 机制**\n- 核心问题：cron 先加再清理，可能短暂超过 TARGET+BUFFER\n- blocklist 机制：手动删除 entity 需同步加 blocklist\n- 解决：prune 时自动追加 blocklist，手动加需用户自己处理\n\n### 5轮评审发现（本次）\n\n| 轮次 | 发现 | 严重性 |\n|------|------|--------|\n| R1 | auto-score-classify HOOK.md 示例 JSON 用旧格式 | P0 ✅ 已修 |\n| R2 | blocklist 子串误匹配（`agent` 匹配 `agent-team-orchestration`） | P0 ✅ 已修 |\n| R3 | 两个 context.json（全局 vs session级）设计如此，无需改 | P0 已知 |\n| R4 | bootstrap hook 逻辑完整，getLatestSessionSummary 正确 | P1 ✅ 已验证 |\n| R5 | 所有运行时代码无 3104 残留，仅注释中有 | P0 ✅ 已清 |\n\n### 当前稳定状态\n\n| 组件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| gateway | ✅ pid 170136, port 3001 |\n| 3103 scorer | ✅ pid 57453 |\n| 3105 scene-classifier v2 | ✅ pid 88283 |\n| entities | ✅ 31个（目标28-31） |\n| blocklist | ✅ 15个唯一条目 |\n| wiki-learn cron | ✅ delivery:none |\n| openclaw-router | ✅ 已杀，systemd disable |\n| 3101 端口 | ✅ 释放 |\n\n### 待验证\n- [ ] 下次 /new 时 bootstrap hook 真实注入 session-summary\n- [ ] session-summary hook 生成真实摘要（非手动创建的文件）\n- [ ] cron 验证 entities 稳定在28-31\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776082297410}}
