{"type":"message","id":"1fea3ad5","parentId":"e7ff671d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:15:33.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very comprehensive understanding of the project. Let me compile the full picture.\n\nThe project at D:\\aafuzhi\\axs has TWO separate apps:\n\n1. **Root level (`番茄创作工作台`)** - Electron app with:\n   - `src/main/index.ts` - Electron main process (424 lines)\n   - `src/preload/` - Preload scripts\n   - `src/renderer/src/components/` - 5 components: AIToolsPanel, Editor, FactsPanel, OutlineTree, Workbench\n   - `src/renderer/src/services/` - 2 services: aiModels.ts (155 lines), factExtractor.ts (172 lines)\n   - Uses Zustand for state, Ant Design for UI, Monaco Editor for editing\n   - Currently in development (dist/ exists)\n\n2. **`novel-desktop-app/`** - More mature Electron app with:\n   - 30+ components including CharacterManager, PlotPlanner, SettingManager, PolishAssistant, etc.\n   - Massive services: aiService.ts (1606 lines), promptStore.ts (933 lines)\n   - ConsistencyChecker, ChartVisualization, RhythmPanel, FactsManager, ProjectManager\n   - Same tech stack: Electron + React + Ant Design + Zustand\n   - Also has dist/\n\n3. **`my-novel-tools/`** - CLI tools (10 command line tools):\n   - personality, fear, structure, world-seed, complement, catharsis, emotion, template, dialogue, generate-chapter\n   - Each tool is a separate JS file in bin/\n\n4. **`my-novel/`** - Example/template novel project structure\n\nThe requirement document maps to the overall vision, but there's a disconnect: the root-level Electron app is basic with limited AI tools, while `novel-desktop-app/` is where the substantial implementation lives with CharacterManager, PlotPlanner, SettingManager, PolishAssistant, and dozens of other modules handling the actual creative writing workflow.","thinkingSignature":"8455d1782bb66dbea462282cfdc24a03e6952d3388f64344a433091be6b73c20"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 看完整个项目了，情况比较复杂——**这是两个 Electron App + 一套 CLI 工具**，实施进度参差不齐：\n\n---\n\n## 📁 项目结构\n\n| 目录 | 性质 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/` 根目录 | Electron App (番茄创作工作台) | 🟡 基础框架，功能有限 |\n| `novel-desktop-app/` | 成熟版 Electron App | 🟢 30+ 组件，功能完整 |\n| `my-novel-tools/bin/` | 10个 CLI 创作工具 | 🟢 全部实现并测试通过 |\n| `my-novel/` | 示例小说项目模板 | 🟢 结构完整 |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 需求文档 vs 实际实现\n\n**需求文档的 14 个模块**，落地情况：\n\n| 模块 | 需求 | 实际落地 | 状态 |\n|------|------|----------|------|\n| 多模型支持 | DeepSeek/GPT/Claude/Ollama | 只接了豆包+DeepSeek Reasoner | 🟡 |\n| AI续写/重写/润色 | 完整创作流 | `my-novel-tools` 有 `generate-chapter`，`novel-desktop-app` 有 PolishAssistant | 🟡 |\n| 人物管理 | 关系图/成长跟踪 | `CharacterManager.tsx` (1062行)，关系图谱有 | 🟢 |\n| 章节管理 | 拖拽排序/导入导出 | `OutlineTree` + `ChapterWorkspace` | 🟡 |\n| 事实库系统 | 自动提取/语义搜索 | `factExtractor.ts` + `FactsManager` | 🟢 |\n| 伏笔系统 | 标记/跟踪/回收率 | `ConsistencyChecker.tsx` 有伏笔检测 | 🟡 |\n| AI协作/多Agent | 讨论/头脑风暴 | 未见实现 | 🔴 |\n| 风格迁移 | 作家风格模仿 | 未见实现 | 🔴 |\n| 向量知识库 | 语义搜索 | 引了 `vectra` 但未集成 | 🔴 |\n| 可视化工具 | 关系图/仪表板 | `ChartVisualization.tsx` + `graphology` | 🟡 |\n| 导出EPUB/MD | 导出功能 | 未见实现 | 🔴 |\n| 备份恢复 | 自动备份 | 有 `backupService.ts` | 🟡 |\n| 第三方集成 | Git/云存储 | 未见实现 | 🔴 |\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ 主要问题\n\n1. **根目录 App 功能太弱**——只有 5 个组件，AI 工具只有续写/扩写/逻辑校验/提取事实，需求文档里大部分功能没做\n2. **两个 App 并存**——`novel-desktop-app/` 明显更成熟，但根目录的 `package.json` 指向的是根目录的 Electron 构建，没有统一\n3. **数据库设计有问题**——`db/index.ts` 里用 `window.electronAPI.ai.call(sql)` 来执行 SQL，但 AI 接口是给模型调用的，不是数据库操作\n4. **向量库/语义搜索**——引了 `@xenova/transformers` 和 `vectra`，但没看到实际使用\n5. **导出功能缺失**——需求文档的 EPUB/MD 导出完全没做\n\n---\n\n你想先修哪个方向？数据库问题、App 统一、还是具体功能实现？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29788,"output":1126,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50176,"cost":{"input":0.008936399999999999,"output":0.0013511999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01144332}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776082498222,"responseId":"062c114158f4140047928140bff1b61c"}}
