{"type":"message","id":"3c921bfd","parentId":"390a1abd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:27:15.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So `graphology` is NOT installed in `novel-desktop-app/node_modules/` but it IS in the root `node_modules/`. But the renderer code in `novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/lib/graphAnalysis.ts` imports from `graphology`. If the renderer is built with vite and runs in a browser context (not Node.js), it won't have access to `node_modules` directly - vite would need to bundle it. But vite's `external` configuration might not be set up for this.\n\nActually wait - the renderer runs in the Electron BrowserWindow, and with vite bundling, it would bundle the graphology library into the output JS. \n\nSince graphology isn't in `novel-desktop-app/package.json` as a dependency, vite can't resolve it during the build, so the import will fail at runtime even though the compiled renderer code might be sitting in `dist/renderer/assets/`. Meanwhile, the root `package.json` does list graphology, but the build command is running from `novel-desktop-app/` using its own config, not the root.\n\nSo I've found all the critical issues blocking the app from running: the entry point path is wrong, the HTML file path is wrong, critical dependencies are missing from the package.json, and graphology isn't available where the build expects it.","thinkingSignature":"772abf24c4f5e5641b8f1943373cdd57c5120b98a39954fa760894af519e824d"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好，这次彻底翻了一遍。发现的问题比我之前说的还要严重 10 倍：\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 致命问题（完全无法运行）\n\n### 1. `package.json` 入口路径错误\n\n```json\n\"main\": \"dist/main/src/main/main.js\"   // 这个路径不存在！\n```\n\n`tsconfig.node.json` 的 `outDir: \"dist/main\"` + `include: [\"src/main\"]` → TypeScript 推算 `rootDir: \"src\"`。实际输出：\n```\ndist/main/main/main.js    ← 实际位置\ndist/main/main/preload.js\n```\n不是 `dist/main/src/main/`。\n\n### 2. HTML 加载路径错误\n\n`main.ts` 第 104 行：\n```ts\nmainWindow.loadFile(path.join(__dirname, '../../../index.html'))\n// __dirname = dist/main/main/\n// → dist/index.html  ← 存在，但实际资源在 dist/renderer/\n```\n\n正确路径应该是 `dist/renderer/index.html`（向上 4 层而非 3 层）。\n\n### 3. 图标路径错误\n\n```ts\nicon: path.join(__dirname, '../../assets/icon.ico')\n// → dist/assets/icon.ico  ← 不存在\n// 实际：novel-desktop-app/assets/icon.ico\n```\n\n### 4. 关键依赖缺失\n\n`novel-desktop-app/package.json` 缺少运行时依赖：\n```\nelectron-store   ← 代码中 dynamic import，但 package.json 无此依赖\ngraphology       ← graphAnalysis.ts 直接 import，但 package.json 无\n@xenova/transformers  ← 向量库，引了但没装\nvectra            ← 同上\nbetter-sqlite3   ← db/index.ts 提到，但从未安装\n```\n\n根目录 `package.json` 有这些依赖，但 `novel-desktop-app/` 是独立目录，有自己的 `node_modules`，**没有这些包**。\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 两套代码严重重复\n\n| 目录 | 主进程 | preload | 渲染进程 | 状态 |\n|------|--------|---------|---------|------|\n| `/src/` (根) | `index.ts`（引用不存在的 aiService） | `index.ts` ✅ | 基础版（5组件） | ❌ 缺 AI |\n| `/novel-desktop-app/src/` | `main.ts` + `index.ts` ✅ | `preload.ts` ✅ | 完整版（30+ 组件） | ❌ 入口路径错 |\n\n两个 `src/main/index.ts` 内容**完全相同**（我用 diff 验证过），都引用不存在的 `aiService.ts`（在根目录的 `src/main/` 里）。但 `novel-desktop-app/src/main/` 里有真正的 `aiService.ts`。\n\n---\n\n## 🔴 数据层彻底错误\n\n`db/index.ts`（两个版本都是）：\n\n```ts\n// ❌ 错误：把 SQL 发给 AI API 执行\nawait window.electronAPI.ai.call(insertSQL, { type: 'sql' })\n\n// ❌ 注释说要 better-sqlite3，实际没装也没用\n// 在 Electron 环境中使用 better-sqlite3\n```\n\nSQL 执行走了 AI 服务，AI 不是数据库。SQLite 从未实现。\n\n---\n\n## 🟡 Build 流程断节\n\n```\n根目录 package.json:\n  \"main\": \"dist/main/index.js\"    ← 指向 128 行老版本（compiled）\n  引用 require('./aiService') 但 dist 版本没有\n\nnovel-desktop-app:\n  \"main\": \"dist/main/src/main/main.js\"  ← 路径不存在\n  npm run build:main (tsc) 从未单独跑过\n  npm run build (vite) 只 build 了 renderer\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完整问题汇总\n\n| # | 问题 | 严重度 | 位置 |\n|---|------|--------|------|\n| 1 | 入口路径错误 | 🔴 | `package.json` |\n| 2 | HTML 加载差一层目录 | 🔴 | `main.ts:104` |\n| 3 | 图标路径错误 | 🟡 | `main.ts:95` |\n| 4 | electron-store 未声明依赖 | 🔴 | `package.json` |\n| 5 | graphology/@xenova/transformers 未声明 | 🔴 | `package.json` |\n| 6 | SQLite 实现是假的（走 AI API） | 🔴 | `db/index.ts` |\n| 7 | 根目录 src/main 引用不存在模块 | 🔴 | `src/main/index.ts` |\n| 8 | 两套 preload 不一致 | 🟡 | 根 vs novel-desktop-app |\n| 9 | vite dev 端口 3000 vs 3004 | 🟡 | `main.ts:100` vs `vite.config.ts` |\n| 10 | 向量库 build 脚本为空 | 🟡 | `build-vector-index.js` |\n\n---\n\n**结论**：这不是\"功能没做完\"，是**整个 build 从来没有完整跑通过**。源码是完整的，但工程化层面全是断点。需要从修复入口路径和依赖声明开始，重新打通 build。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":71069,"output":1324,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91655,"cost":{"input":0.021320699999999998,"output":0.0015888,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02406522}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776083197902,"responseId":"062c13fde29debae7e6fa81acd5ced47"}}
