{"type":"message","id":"d41037c0","parentId":"110a04b4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:30:43.234Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now do a final check on what's really implemented vs requirements. I have a good enough picture now. Let me compile the comprehensive findings.\n\nHere's what I know:\n\n**COMPLETED features:**\n1. Multi-model AI: doubao, deepseek, kimi, openai, ollama - AI service layer complete\n2. AI Tools Panel (续写/扩写/逻辑校验/提取事实)\n3. Character Manager (CRUD + AI generation of attributes)\n4. Facts Manager (extract, store, verify)\n5. Setting Manager (世界观 with AI generation)\n6. Outline View + Plot Planner + Batch Processor\n7. Consistency Checker (矛盾检测, 逻辑校验, 伏笔跟踪)\n\n\n8. Rhythm Panel (情绪节奏), Chart Visualization (line/pie/bar/radar charts), Project Manager (multi-project, version history via localStorage), and Notes Manager (灵感发散)\n9. Polish Assistant and rhythm/quality checking tools, plus Backup Service integration\n\n**MISSING or INCOMPLETE:**\n1. **EPUB/Markdown Export** - completely missing\n2. **Style Transfer (风格迁移)** - `style_imitation` is in FunctionName type but I don't see actual UI implementation for it\n3. **Multi-Agent Discussion (多Agent讨论)** - not implemented\n4. **Brainstorming** - NotesManager has inspiration tools but no real multi-agent brainstorming\n5. **Vector/Semantic Search (向量语义搜索)** - vectra and @xenova/transformers imported but never used; the `setting_recall` function maps to AI but actual vector store not integrated\n6. **Cross-device Sync (跨设备同步)** - completely fake (simulates 2 second delay, hardcoded fake devices)\n7. **Plugin System (插件系统)** - not implemented\n8. **Character Relationship Graph Visualization** - no dedicated visualization component for character relationships; ChartVisualization has emotion/catharsis charts only\n9. **Character Growth Arc Visualization** - mentioned in prompts but not visually tracked or displayed\n10. **Git/Version Control Integration** - ProjectManager has version history stored in localStorage, not actual git\n11. **Cloud Backup** - backup service exists for local file backup only, no cloud integration\n12. **Foreshadow Board UI (伏笔板)** - tracked in consistencyChecker logic but no dedicated看板-style UI\n13. **Worldview Consistency Check Automation** - needs to be triggered manually rather than running automatically on save\n14. **Plot Relation Graph Visualization** - character relationships are defined but there's no visual network graph component for them\n\nI'm also noticing that `vectra` and `better-sqlite3` are listed as dependencies but haven't been installed yet. Let me double-check if style_imitation is actually implemented somewhere.","thinkingSignature":"bf414fbb4d918bb217563e0f0f2c999ec5170f99c88a7bac7829393236685d1f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q2auctkofon8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rn \"style_imitation\\|style.*lock\\|风格锁定\\|writer.*imitation\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src --include=\"*.ts\" --include=\"*.tsx\" -n 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q2auctkofon8_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -rn \"writing_style_locked\\|style_locked_continuation\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src --include=\"*.ts\" --include=\"*.tsx\" -n 2>/dev/null | head -10"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q2auctkofon8_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"api.*key\\|apiKey\\|saveApiKey\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/main/aiService.ts | head -20"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":76642,"output":784,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96688,"cost":{"input":0.0229926,"output":0.0009408,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025089119999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776083421913,"responseId":"062c14dc91ebd3f096bdff1d09c3f19c"}}
