{"type":"message","id":"f9e40a40","parentId":"3c21cda0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:33:39.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both Workbench.tsx files are identical (same size, diff shows no output). And neither is imported/used in the App.tsx. So:\n\n1. `Workbench.tsx` exists in both `src/components/` directories but is NEVER imported anywhere\n2. The actual \"workspace\" functionality uses `ChapterWorkspace.tsx`\n\nSo the user's point about missing \"创作工作台\" - the Workbench component exists but is completely unused. It's a dead component. And the actual ChapterWorkspace is what's being used.\n\nBut maybe the user means something different - perhaps the \"创作工作台\" is supposed to be a more comprehensive writing workspace that's not fully implemented? Let me re-read the Workbench component to see what it was meant to do vs what's actually being used.","thinkingSignature":"79bd91992ba7cd4edcc4dad510ec5b71d99f590d96700e365ab41c5ad166f326"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g2kzus5hh6ve_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/Workbench.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":81024,"output":206,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100492,"cost":{"input":0.024307199999999998,"output":0.0002472,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025710119999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776083611571,"responseId":"062c159b429e4ed01a9efd5f2236b772"}}
{"type":"message","id":"9f48ee66","parentId":"f9e40a40","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:33:40.024Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_g2kzus5hh6ve_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Layout, Menu, Button, message } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SaveOutlined,\n  FolderOpenOutlined,\n  BookOutlined,\n  UserOutlined,\n  SettingOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport OutlineTree from './OutlineTree'\nimport Editor from './Editor'\nimport FactsPanel from './FactsPanel'\nimport AIToolsPanel from './AIToolsPanel'\nimport type { MenuProps } from 'antd'\n\nconst { Sider, Content } = Layout\n\ntype TabKey = 'outline' | 'characters' | 'settings' | 'facts' | 'ai'\n\n// 左侧菜单\nconst siderMenuItems: MenuProps['items'] = [\n  { key: 'outline', icon: <BookOutlined />, label: '大纲导航' },\n  { key: 'characters', icon: <UserOutlined />, label: '角色管理' },\n  { key: 'settings', icon: <SettingOutlined />, label: '世界设定' },\n  { key: 'facts', icon: <ThunderboltOutlined />, label: '事实台账' },\n]\n\nconst Workbench = () => {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<TabKey>('outline')\n  const [activeChapter, setActiveChapter] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [chapterContent, setChapterContent] = useState('')\n  const [projectRoot, setProjectRoot] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [isDirty, setIsDirty] = useState(false)\n  const [autoSaveTimer, setAutoSaveTimer] = useState<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null)\n\n  // 初始化项目\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const init = async () => {\n      const root = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      setProjectRoot(root)\n    }\n    init()\n  }, [])\n\n  // 自动保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (isDirty && activeChapter) {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n      \n      const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n        handleSave()\n      }, 5000) // 5秒防抖自动保存\n      \n      setAutoSaveTimer(timer)\n    }\n\n    return () => {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n    }\n  }, [chapterContent, isDirty])\n\n  // 打开项目\n  const handleOpenProject = async () => {\n    const directory = await window.electronAPI.openDirectory()\n    if (directory) {\n      setProjectRoot(directory)\n      message.success(`已打开项目：${directory}`)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 保存章节\n  const handleSave = async () => {\n    if (!activeChapter || !chapterContent) return\n\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(activeChapter, chapterContent)\n      if (result.success) {\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        message.success('已保存')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败：${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('保存失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 章节选择\n  const handleChapterSelect = async (filePath: string) => {\n    if (isDirty) {\n      // 提示保存\n      const confirm = window.confirm('当前章节有未保存的内容，是否保存？')\n      if (confirm) await handleSave()\n    }\n\n    setActiveChapter(filePath)\n    \n    // 读取章节内容\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(filePath)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        setChapterContent(result.content)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('读取章节失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 内容变化\n  const handleContentChange = (value: string | undefined) => {\n    if (value === undefined) return\n    setChapterContent(value)\n    setIsDirty(true)\n  }\n\n  // 快捷键保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 's') {\n        e.preventDefault()\n        handleSave()\n      }\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n    return () => window.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n  }, [activeChapter, chapterContent])\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ height: '100vh' }}>\n      {/* 顶部工具栏 */}\n      <Layout.Header\n        style={{\n          display: 'flex',\n          alignItems: 'center',\n          padding: '0 20px',\n          background: '#fff',\n          borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8',\n          justifyContent: 'space-between'\n        }}\n      >\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 20 }}>\n          <h2 style={{ margin: 0 }}>🍅 番茄小说创作助手</h2>\n          {projectRoot && <span style={{ color: '#999' }}>当前项目：{projectRoot}</span>}\n        </div>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 10 }}>\n          <Button\n            icon={<FolderOpenOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleOpenProject}\n          >\n            打开项目\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            icon={<SaveOutlined />}\n            type=\"primary\"\n            onClick={handleSave}\n            disabled={!isDirty || !activeChapter}\n          >\n            保存 {isDirty ? '*' : ''}\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </Layout.Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        {/* 左侧边栏 */}\n        <Sider width={64} theme=\"light\">\n          <Menu\n            mode=\"inline\"\n            selectedKeys={[activeTab]}\n            items={siderMenuItems}\n            onClick={({ key }) => setActiveTab(key as TabKey)}\n            style={{ height: '100%', borderRight: 0 }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 左侧内容区 */}\n        <Sider width={280} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          {activeTab === 'outline' && projectRoot && (\n            <OutlineTree\n              projectRoot={projectRoot}\n              activeChapter={activeChapter}\n              onSelect={handleChapterSelect}\n            />\n          )}\n          {activeTab === 'characters' && <div>角色管理（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'settings' && <div>世界设定（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'facts' && <FactsPanel />}\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 中间编辑区 */}\n        <Content style={{ background: '#fff' }}>\n          {activeChapter ? (\n            <Editor\n              value={chapterContent}\n              onChange={handleContentChange}\n              filePath={activeChapter}\n            />\n          ) : (\n            <div\n              style={{\n                display: 'flex',\n                height: '100%',\n                alignItems: 'center',\n                justifyContent: 'center',\n                color: '#999',\n                fontSize: 18,\n              }}\n            >\n              请在左侧选择章节，或打开一个小说项目\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* 右侧AI工具区 */}\n        <Sider width={320} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderLeft: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          <AIToolsPanel\n            chapterContent={chapterContent}\n            chapterPath={activeChapter}\n            onInsertText={(text) => {\n              // 插入到编辑器光标位置\n              setChapterContent(prev => prev + text)\n              setIsDirty(true)\n            }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default Workbench"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":49,"aggregated":"import { useState, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { Layout, Menu, Button, message } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SaveOutlined,\n  FolderOpenOutlined,\n  BookOutlined,\n  UserOutlined,\n  SettingOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport OutlineTree from './OutlineTree'\nimport Editor from './Editor'\nimport FactsPanel from './FactsPanel'\nimport AIToolsPanel from './AIToolsPanel'\nimport type { MenuProps } from 'antd'\n\nconst { Sider, Content } = Layout\n\ntype TabKey = 'outline' | 'characters' | 'settings' | 'facts' | 'ai'\n\n// 左侧菜单\nconst siderMenuItems: MenuProps['items'] = [\n  { key: 'outline', icon: <BookOutlined />, label: '大纲导航' },\n  { key: 'characters', icon: <UserOutlined />, label: '角色管理' },\n  { key: 'settings', icon: <SettingOutlined />, label: '世界设定' },\n  { key: 'facts', icon: <ThunderboltOutlined />, label: '事实台账' },\n]\n\nconst Workbench = () => {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<TabKey>('outline')\n  const [activeChapter, setActiveChapter] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [chapterContent, setChapterContent] = useState('')\n  const [projectRoot, setProjectRoot] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [isDirty, setIsDirty] = useState(false)\n  const [autoSaveTimer, setAutoSaveTimer] = useState<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null)\n\n  // 初始化项目\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const init = async () => {\n      const root = await window.electronAPI.getProjectRoot()\n      setProjectRoot(root)\n    }\n    init()\n  }, [])\n\n  // 自动保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (isDirty && activeChapter) {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n      \n      const timer = setTimeout(() => {\n        handleSave()\n      }, 5000) // 5秒防抖自动保存\n      \n      setAutoSaveTimer(timer)\n    }\n\n    return () => {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n    }\n  }, [chapterContent, isDirty])\n\n  // 打开项目\n  const handleOpenProject = async () => {\n    const directory = await window.electronAPI.openDirectory()\n    if (directory) {\n      setProjectRoot(directory)\n      message.success(`已打开项目：${directory}`)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 保存章节\n  const handleSave = async () => {\n    if (!activeChapter || !chapterContent) return\n\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(activeChapter, chapterContent)\n      if (result.success) {\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        message.success('已保存')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败：${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('保存失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 章节选择\n  const handleChapterSelect = async (filePath: string) => {\n    if (isDirty) {\n      // 提示保存\n      const confirm = window.confirm('当前章节有未保存的内容，是否保存？')\n      if (confirm) await handleSave()\n    }\n\n    setActiveChapter(filePath)\n    \n    // 读取章节内容\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(filePath)\n      if (result.success && result.content) {\n        setChapterContent(result.content)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('读取章节失败')\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 内容变化\n  const handleContentChange = (value: string | undefined) => {\n    if (value === undefined) return\n    setChapterContent(value)\n    setIsDirty(true)\n  }\n\n  // 快捷键保存\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 's') {\n        e.preventDefault()\n        handleSave()\n      }\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n    return () => window.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n  }, [activeChapter, chapterContent])\n\n  return (\n    <Layout style={{ height: '100vh' }}>\n      {/* 顶部工具栏 */}\n      <Layout.Header\n        style={{\n          display: 'flex',\n          alignItems: 'center',\n          padding: '0 20px',\n          background: '#fff',\n          borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8',\n          justifyContent: 'space-between'\n        }}\n      >\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 20 }}>\n          <h2 style={{ margin: 0 }}>🍅 番茄小说创作助手</h2>\n          {projectRoot && <span style={{ color: '#999' }}>当前项目：{projectRoot}</span>}\n        </div>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 10 }}>\n          <Button\n            icon={<FolderOpenOutlined />}\n            onClick={handleOpenProject}\n          >\n            打开项目\n          </Button>\n          <Button\n            icon={<SaveOutlined />}\n            type=\"primary\"\n            onClick={handleSave}\n            disabled={!isDirty || !activeChapter}\n          >\n            保存 {isDirty ? '*' : ''}\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </Layout.Header>\n\n      <Layout>\n        {/* 左侧边栏 */}\n        <Sider width={64} theme=\"light\">\n          <Menu\n            mode=\"inline\"\n            selectedKeys={[activeTab]}\n            items={siderMenuItems}\n            onClick={({ key }) => setActiveTab(key as TabKey)}\n            style={{ height: '100%', borderRight: 0 }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 左侧内容区 */}\n        <Sider width={280} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          {activeTab === 'outline' && projectRoot && (\n            <OutlineTree\n              projectRoot={projectRoot}\n              activeChapter={activeChapter}\n              onSelect={handleChapterSelect}\n            />\n          )}\n          {activeTab === 'characters' && <div>角色管理（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'settings' && <div>世界设定（开发中）</div>}\n          {activeTab === 'facts' && <FactsPanel />}\n        </Sider>\n\n        {/* 中间编辑区 */}\n        <Content style={{ background: '#fff' }}>\n          {activeChapter ? (\n            <Editor\n              value={chapterContent}\n              onChange={handleContentChange}\n              filePath={activeChapter}\n            />\n          ) : (\n            <div\n              style={{\n                display: 'flex',\n                height: '100%',\n                alignItems: 'center',\n                justifyContent: 'center',\n                color: '#999',\n                fontSize: 18,\n              }}\n            >\n              请在左侧选择章节，或打开一个小说项目\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </Content>\n\n        {/* 右侧AI工具区 */}\n        <Sider width={320} theme=\"light\" style={{ borderLeft: '1px solid #e8e8e8' }}>\n          <AIToolsPanel\n            chapterContent={chapterContent}\n            chapterPath={activeChapter}\n            onInsertText={(text) => {\n              // 插入到编辑器光标位置\n              setChapterContent(prev => prev + text)\n              setIsDirty(true)\n            }}\n          />\n        </Sider>\n      </Layout>\n    </Layout>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default Workbench","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776083620013}}
{"type":"message","id":"22a008a1","parentId":"9f48ee66","timestamp":"2026-04-13T12:34:02.305Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture:\n\n1. `Workbench.tsx` - a full-featured standalone layout with sidebar navigation, chapter editor, and AI tools panel. It imports `OutlineTree`, `Editor`, `FactsPanel`, `AIToolsPanel`. This is a well-designed layout that looks like a proper writing workbench.\n\n2. But this `Workbench.tsx` is **never imported or used** anywhere in the app. It's a dead component.\n\n3. The `ChapterWorkspace.tsx` is what's actually used for the workspace, but it's a different component with different architecture.\n\nSo the user is right - the \"创作工作台\" exists as `Workbench.tsx` but it's completely orphaned (never used). The actual \"workspace\" in the app uses `ChapterWorkspace` which is a different component.\n   \nThe `ChapterWorkspace` feels like a draft compared to `Workbench` - certain features like world building and character management are marked as \"in development\" while the full workbench version was built out but never integrated. Looking at the menu structure, \"创作工作台\" is actually mapped to `ChapterWorkspace` in the app, not `Workbench`, so there's a naming mismatch - the component that should be the workbench is `Workbench.tsx` but it's been replaced by a less complete alternative.","thinkingSignature":"ec04a7a96c1d8162fc34c8348a3968a3b52bd3971436ceefcc02f75280025f3a"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，而且问题更糟——\n\n**`Workbench.tsx` 根本没用上。**\n\n存在两个创作工作台：\n\n| 组件 | 文件 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `Workbench.tsx` | 232行，三栏布局（大纲+编辑器+AI工具） | **死代码**，从未被 import |\n| `ChapterWorkspace.tsx` | 361行，实际被 App.tsx 引用 | 在用，但功能比 Workbench 弱 |\n\n```tsx\n// App.tsx 里的 workspace 菜单 → 实际渲染的是 ChapterWorkspace\ncase 'workspace':\n  return <ChapterWorkspace ... />  // ← 不是 Workbench\n\n// Workbench.tsx 存在但从未出现\nimport Workbench from './components/Workbench'  // ← 这行根本不存在\n```\n\n**`Workbench.tsx` 的现状：**\n- 三栏布局（左侧大纲 / 中间编辑器 / 右侧AI工具）✅\n- 自动保存 ✅\n- `OutlineTree` + `Editor` + `FactsPanel` + `AIToolsPanel` 全部引用 ✅\n- 但 `角色管理` 和 `世界设定` 两个 tab 是假的：**直接写死中文\"开发中\"**\n\n```tsx\n// Workbench.tsx 第176-177行\n{activeTab === 'characters' && <div>角色管理（开发中）</div>}\n{activeTab === 'settings' && <div>世界设定（开发中）</div>}\n```\n\n**所以真实情况：**\n- `Workbench.tsx` 是完整的**布局框架**，但两个核心 tab 是空壳\n- `ChapterWorkspace` 是**实际在用的**，功能更完整，但没有用 Workbench 的布局\n- 两个组件重复，Workbench 是废弃的半成品\n\n要我整合这两个？还是直接废弃 Workbench，把 ChapterWorkspace 做成完整的三栏布局？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82936,"output":669,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102867,"cost":{"input":0.024880799999999998,"output":0.0008028,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.026839319999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776083620027,"responseId":"062c15a3d8454107bc099e02fd884db9"}}
