{"type":"message","id":"918b9d91","parentId":"6661270c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:08:49.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the interfaces match what I used in IntegratedWorkbench. But wait, in my `handleSave` callback, I'm passing `handleSave` directly to `MarkdownEditor` and `YAMLEditor`. But `handleSave` takes no arguments (it reads from `currentFile` and `frontmatter` state), while `onSave` expects `(content: string) => Promise<void>`. That's a mismatch!\n\nIn `ChapterWorkspace.tsx`, the save handler was:\n```tsx\n<MarkdownEditor\n  content={parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content).content}\n  onSave={handleSave}\n  filePath={fileName}\n/>\n```\n\nWhere `handleSave` was defined as `handleSave = useCallback(async (editorContent: string) => {...}` - it accepts `editorContent`.\n\n\nI need to fix this - the `onSave` callback passes the editor content directly, but my current `handleSave` ignores that argument and reconstructs the content from state instead. I should align my implementation with what ChapterWorkspace does.","thinkingSignature":"b7bb15c2f8dde4ac8e4d136cd7bd5df8f5265bdeef83ec1fd8491485a3e2b2c8"},{"type":"text","text":"发现一个问题——`MarkdownEditor.onSave` 期望 `(content: string) => Promise<void>`，但我的 `handleSave` 不接受参数。快速修一下：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gh5u8w4yn9mc_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/IntegratedWorkbench.tsx","edits":[{"oldText":"  // 保存文件\n  const handleSave = useCallback(async () => {\n    if (!currentFile) return\n    setIsSaving(true)\n    try {\n      const parsed = parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content)\n      const fullContent = stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, parsed.content)\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(currentFile.path, fullContent)\n      if (result.success) {\n        openFile(currentFile.path, fullContent)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        setLastSaved(new Date())\n        message.success('保存成功')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败: ${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('保存文件失败')\n    } finally {\n      setIsSaving(false)\n    }\n  }, [currentFile, frontmatter, openFile])","newText":"  // 保存文件（支持从编辑器直接传入内容）\n  const handleSave = useCallback(async (editorContent?: string) => {\n    if (!currentFile) return\n    setIsSaving(true)\n    try {\n      // 如果传入了编辑器内容，用它；否则从 state 重建\n      const contentToSave = editorContent !== undefined\n        ? stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, editorContent)\n        : stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content).content)\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(currentFile.path, contentToSave)\n      if (result.success) {\n        openFile(currentFile.path, contentToSave)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        setLastSaved(new Date())\n        message.success('保存成功')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败: ${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch (error) {\n      message.error('保存文件失败')\n    } finally {\n      setIsSaving(false)\n    }\n  }, [currentFile, frontmatter, openFile])"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":110693,"output":750,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130705,"cost":{"input":0.0332079,"output":0.0009,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.035263619999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776085712014,"responseId":"062c1dcf6671a37eb3aa3ea3f63fa1c1"}}
