{"type":"message","id":"1eef2776","parentId":"8f342433","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:34:11.734Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ad05m9nu1dr7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\r\nimport path from 'path'\r\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\r\nimport { WebContents } from 'electron'\r\n\r\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\r\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null\r\n\r\n// 项目根目录 - 用于路径验证\r\nlet projectRootPath: string | null = null\r\n\r\n// 文件系统监视器\r\nlet fsWatcher: FSWatcher | null = null\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 验证文件路径是否安全\r\n * 防止路径遍历攻击 (如 ../../../etc/passwd)\r\n * 只允许访问项目目录内的文件\r\n */\r\nfunction validatePath(requestedPath: string): { valid: boolean; resolvedPath?: string; error?: string } {\r\n  // 如果没有设置项目根路径，允许绝对路径但进行基本验证\r\n  if (!projectRootPath) {\r\n    // 解析并规范化路径\r\n    const resolved = path.resolve(requestedPath)\r\n    \r\n    // 检查是否尝试访问系统敏感目录\r\n    const sensitivePaths = [\r\n      '/etc',\r\n      '/proc',\r\n      '/sys',\r\n      'C:\\\\Windows',\r\n      'C:\\\\Program Files',\r\n      'C:\\\\Program Files (x86)',\r\n    ]\r\n    \r\n    for (const sensitive of sensitivePaths) {\r\n      if (resolved.toLowerCase().startsWith(sensitive.toLowerCase())) {\r\n        return {\r\n          valid: false,\r\n          error: `访问被拒绝：不允许访问系统目录`,\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return { valid: true, resolvedPath: resolved }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 解析并规范化请求的路径\r\n  const resolved = path.resolve(requestedPath)\r\n  const normalizedRequested = path.normalize(resolved)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":55,"aggregated":"import { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\r\nimport path from 'path'\r\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\r\nimport { WebContents } from 'electron'\r\n\r\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\r\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null\r\n\r\n// 项目根目录 - 用于路径验证\r\nlet projectRootPath: string | null = null\r\n\r\n// 文件系统监视器\r\nlet fsWatcher: FSWatcher | null = null\r\n\r\n/**\r\n * 验证文件路径是否安全\r\n * 防止路径遍历攻击 (如 ../../../etc/passwd)\r\n * 只允许访问项目目录内的文件\r\n */\r\nfunction validatePath(requestedPath: string): { valid: boolean; resolvedPath?: string; error?: string } {\r\n  // 如果没有设置项目根路径，允许绝对路径但进行基本验证\r\n  if (!projectRootPath) {\r\n    // 解析并规范化路径\r\n    const resolved = path.resolve(requestedPath)\r\n    \r\n    // 检查是否尝试访问系统敏感目录\r\n    const sensitivePaths = [\r\n      '/etc',\r\n      '/proc',\r\n      '/sys',\r\n      'C:\\\\Windows',\r\n      'C:\\\\Program Files',\r\n      'C:\\\\Program Files (x86)',\r\n    ]\r\n    \r\n    for (const sensitive of sensitivePaths) {\r\n      if (resolved.toLowerCase().startsWith(sensitive.toLowerCase())) {\r\n        return {\r\n          valid: false,\r\n          error: `访问被拒绝：不允许访问系统目录`,\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    \r\n    return { valid: true, resolvedPath: resolved }\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  // 解析并规范化请求的路径\r\n  const resolved = path.resolve(requestedPath)\r\n  const normalizedRequested = path.normalize(resolved)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776087251725}}
{"type":"message","id":"dec82b71","parentId":"1eef2776","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:34:21.420Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see - main.ts is a big file. It imports from 'electron' and 'fs'. It doesn't import index.ts. But there's clearly some mechanism causing both main.js and index.js to be loaded.\n\nWait - let me think again. The tsconfig.node.json includes BOTH `src/main/main.ts` and `src/main/index.ts` (because it includes `[\"src/main\"]` which is a glob pattern). Both files get compiled to `dist/main/src/main/`. The package.json `\"main\": \"dist/main/src/main/main.js\"` points to main.js.\n\nWhen electron runs `require('dist/main/src/main/main.js')`, it only loads main.js. \n\nBut if index.js was never required, why is it being loaded? Let me reconsider - maybe there's another main.ts in the src/main directory that's actually the entry point, and I need to verify what the tsconfig actually specifies. Let me look at what index.ts and index.js actually contain to understand which one is the main entry point.","thinkingSignature":"f6dd86349032a7d566c943c308c80f4620716394aab7f37081393a4dd9f73dcc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bo503og7nz7g_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -30 /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/main/index.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28741,"output":252,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48255,"cost":{"input":0.0086223,"output":0.0003024,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01008042}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776087251736,"responseId":"062c23d2ed9b81dd35f155448bd7ffd4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"880d8cd3","parentId":"dec82b71","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:34:21.515Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_bo503og7nz7g_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * 番茄小说创作助手 - Electron 主进程入口\n * \n * 提供：\n * - 窗口管理\n * - IPC 处理器注册\n * - 文件系统 API\n * - SQLite 连接（待实现）\n */\n\nimport { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\n\n// 重新导出 main.ts 的功能\n// 这是为了保持统一的导入路径：import { createWindow } from '../src/main/index'\n\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null\n\n// 项目根目录 - 用于路径验证\nlet projectRootPath: string | null = null\n\n// 文件系统监视器\nlet fsWatcher: FSWatcher | null = null\n\n/**\n * 验证文件路径是否安全\n * 防止路径遍历攻击 (如 ../../../etc/passwd)\n * 只允许访问项目目录内的文件"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":59,"aggregated":"/**\n * 番茄小说创作助手 - Electron 主进程入口\n * \n * 提供：\n * - 窗口管理\n * - IPC 处理器注册\n * - 文件系统 API\n * - SQLite 连接（待实现）\n */\n\nimport { app, BrowserWindow, ipcMain, dialog, shell, safeStorage } from 'electron'\nimport path from 'path'\nimport fs, { FSWatcher } from 'fs'\n\n// 重新导出 main.ts 的功能\n// 这是为了保持统一的导入路径：import { createWindow } from '../src/main/index'\n\n// 保持对窗口对象的全局引用，避免被垃圾回收\nlet mainWindow: BrowserWindow | null = null\n\n// 项目根目录 - 用于路径验证\nlet projectRootPath: string | null = null\n\n// 文件系统监视器\nlet fsWatcher: FSWatcher | null = null\n\n/**\n * 验证文件路径是否安全\n * 防止路径遍历攻击 (如 ../../../etc/passwd)\n * 只允许访问项目目录内的文件","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/main"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776087261503}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d92b811","parentId":"880d8cd3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:34:36.958Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both `main.ts` and `index.ts` are separate entry points and they both register the same IPC handlers! The comment says \"重新导出 main.ts 的功能\" but they both have the same code for IPC handlers.\n\nThis is the root cause: TWO files (`main.ts` and `index.ts`) both contain the same IPC handler registration code. When the project is compiled, BOTH are compiled. But package.json only points to `main.js`. HOWEVER, there's no reason for index.js to be loaded UNLESS something in electron's startup mechanism is loading it.\n\nWait - let me re-read the error: \"App threw an error during load\". This is at the very start of Electron loading. \n\nSo if only main.js is specified as the entry point in package.json, index.js shouldn't even be touched. Unless the problem isn't a loading issue at all - maybe the duplicate handler registration is happening because both files have their own `ipcMain.handle('fs:writeFile', ...)` calls embedded in them. When main.js runs and sets up its handlers, if it's somehow also triggering index.js's code to execute, that would explain the conflict. But that doesn't make sense unless index.js is actually being required somewhere.\n\nActually, I think I've been misunderstanding this. The error at line 524 of main.js is pointing to the ACTUAL handler registration - so main.js itself is trying to register 'fs:writeFile' twice. That means main.js probably has this handler defined in multiple places, or it's being registered in a module that's loaded multiple times. The fact that the second handler registration fails means the first one succeeded, so the duplicate must be happening within main.js itself or through some module reloading mechanism.","thinkingSignature":"aefc15d0f26a527d532dff02cee29c0cb1304b90b9a9f420ed3a52cc4b692f8e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_y5ab6whvfva8_1","nam