{"type":"message","id":"54a536c3","parentId":"c83a3916","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:59:25.175Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the structure uses a proper nested Layout approach:\n- Outer Layout (height: 100vh) with Header + inner Layout\n- Inner Layout (flex: 1, minHeight: 0) with 4 children: icon Sider (64px), left content Sider (280px), Content, right Sider (360px)\n\nThis should properly distribute the space. The key fixes:\n1. `flex: 1, minHeight: 0` on the inner Layout to fill remaining height\n2. `overflow: hidden` on the icon Sider to prevent it from expanding\n3. `minHeight: 0, overflow: 'hidden'` on Content to prevent flex overflow\n\n\n4. The Content component needs `overflow: 'hidden'` so the MarkdownEditor (which is a tall CodeMirror inside a scrollable div) doesn't cause the content area to expand beyond its bounds.","thinkingSignature":"df0c5e49ea4f6d58c43a6299af0802f0332fb00c5e4d5e166f048e4a99c3c681"},{"type":"text","text":"\n重写了布局，用正确的 flex 嵌套。在 Windows 上重新跑：\n\n```\nnpm start\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42919,"output":206,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62387,"cost":{"input":0.012875699999999999,"output":0.0002472,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014278619999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776088757661,"responseId":"062c29b4f21605530bc18fd5b8392b4b"}}
