{"type":"message","id":"0fc24f9c","parentId":"33a2ab7c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:06:47.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. The App.tsx bundled in index-9d2bce47.js contains references to IntegratedWorkbench. The build is correct.\n\nNow let me think about why only the left icon menu is showing. The user said \"左边一竖排的功能\" - a vertical row of icons on the left. This means:\n1. The 64px icon Sider is visible\n2. But the other 3 panels (280px left, Content, 360px right) are not visible\n\nThis could be because:\n1. The outer Layout has `height: 100vh` but the inner Layout doesn't have proper flex layout\n2. The `flex: 1, minHeight: 0` on the inner Layout might not work as expected\n\n\n3. The Content area might be collapsing to zero width\n\nLooking at my latest code, the inner Layout has `flex: 1, minHeight: 0` which should work for flex children, but the Content component with `minHeight: 0` and `overflow: 'hidden'` might not be receiving proper width allocation from the flex container.\n\nActually, I think the real issue is that I'm using Ant Design's Layout, Sider, and Content components in an atypical way. The outer Layout is correctly set to `height: 100vh`, but I need to verify the inner flex layout is actually propagating the width correctly across all three sections.\n\nLooking at what the user described - just a vertical menu on the left with empty space everywhere else - it seems like only the first Sider is rendering and taking up space, while the Content and right Sider are collapsing to zero width. This suggests the flex distribution isn't working as intended. I should try switching to plain divs with flexbox styling instead of relying on Ant Design's Layout components to see if that resolves the layout issue. I'm examining the file tree structure in the console output and noticing it shows a flat list rather than a nested hierarchy. This suggests the OutlineTree component might be rendering all items at the same level instead of respecting parent-child relationships. The issue could stem from how the data is being passed to the component or how the component itself is configured to display nested content. Looking at the output showing \"左边一竖排的功能\" (just the left icon column), I'm wondering if the issue is actually that `isProjectOpen` or `projectRoot` isn't being set properly, which would cause the app to render the \"请先打开一个项目\" message instead of the actual workbench. Let me trace through the App.tsx logic to see if those props are being passed correctly to IntegratedWorkbench. The project opened successfully at `C:\\Users\\ll\\Documents\\xs` according to the console log, and the CharacterManager loaded 1 character file, so the data is there—but if only the empty state message is rendering, `isProjectOpen` must be false despite the app thinking the project loaded. I'm trying to figure out if `currentPath` and `isProjectOpen` are being set correctly in App.tsx when the project opens, because the workspace isn't showing up even though the project clearly initialized.\n\nThe real issue is that in this desktop Electron app, the renderer process state resets on each page refresh, so `isProjectOpen` gets set to `false` even though the app just opened a project. The user has to manually click the workspace menu item in the left sidebar to switch to it, rather than the app automatically navigating there after opening a project.\n\nLooking at the layout issue though, the left icon menu renders fine but the rest of the layout is empty. This suggests the problem is with the Layout structure itself. I'm considering whether switching to a flexbox approach with plain divs instead of Ant Design's Layout components might fix the rendering issue, since the built files appear correct but the actual display is broken. The 64px Sider renders but the remaining three sections don't, which points to a flexbox distribution problem in how the Layout is structuring its children.","thinkingSignature":"23d41d1e8444d7e1718ed64ac3e8fee73624931bb714562bab624b38fc5018b6"},{"type":"text","text":"Build 成功且正确打包了。现在分析为什么只显示左边一竖排——这是典型的 flex 布局塌陷问题。用纯 flexbox 重写，彻底抛弃嵌套 Sider 的坑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_rmlk81xoahja_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/IntegratedWorkbench.tsx","content":"import React, { useState, useEffect, useCallback, useMemo } from 'react'\nimport { Menu, Button, Typography, Space, Divider, message, Tag, Select } from 'antd'\nimport {\n  SaveOutlined,\n  FolderOpenOutlined,\n  BookOutlined,\n  UserOutlined,\n  SettingOutlined,\n  ThunderboltOutlined,\n  FileTextOutlined,\n  ClockCircleOutlined,\n} from '@ant-design/icons'\nimport type { MenuProps } from 'antd'\nimport OutlineTree from './OutlineTree'\nimport MarkdownEditor from './MarkdownEditor'\nimport YAMLEditor from './YAMLEditor'\nimport CharacterManager from './CharacterManager'\nimport SettingManager from './SettingManager'\nimport FactsPanel from './FactsPanel'\nimport FrontmatterPanel from './FrontmatterPanel'\nimport RelevantFactsPanel from './RelevantFactsPanel'\nimport WorkspaceAITools from './WorkspaceAITools'\nimport { useWorkspaceStore } from '../stores/workspaceStore'\nimport {\n  parseFrontmatter,\n  stringifyFrontmatter,\n  countChineseCharacters,\n  countTotalCharacters,\n  type FrontmatterData,\n} from '../lib/frontmatterParser'\nimport { joinPath } from '../utils/pathUtils'\n\nconst { Title, Text } = Typography\n\ntype TabKey = 'outline' | 'characters' | 'settings' | 'facts'\n\ninterface IntegratedWorkbenchProps {\n  currentPath?: string\n  isProjectOpen?: boolean\n  onClose?: () => void\n}\n\nconst IntegratedWorkbench: React.FC<IntegratedWorkbenchProps> = ({\n  currentPath,\n  isProjectOpen = false,\n}) => {\n  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<TabKey>('outline')\n  const [projectRoot, setProjectRoot] = useState<string | null>(null)\n  const [isDirty, setIsDirty] = useState(false)\n  const [autoSaveTimer, setAutoSaveTimer] = useState<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null)\n  const [characterList, setCharacterList] = useState<Array<{ id: string; name: string; path: string }>>([])\n  const [loadingCharacters, setLoadingCharacters] = useState(false)\n  const [frontmatter, setFrontmatter] = useState<FrontmatterData>({})\n  const [isSaving, setIsSaving] = useState(false)\n  const [lastSaved, setLastSaved] = useState<Date | null>(null)\n\n  const {\n    currentFile,\n    aiOutput,\n    streamingContent,\n    currentCharacter,\n    openFile,\n    setAIOutput,\n    setStreamingContent,\n    setCurrentCharacter,\n  } = useWorkspaceStore()\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (currentPath) setProjectRoot(currentPath)\n  }, [currentPath])\n\n  const loadCharacters = useCallback(async (projectPath: string) => {\n    if (!projectPath) return\n    setLoadingCharacters(true)\n    try {\n      const charsDir = joinPath(projectPath, 'characters')\n      const files = await window.electronAPI.readdir(charsDir)\n      if (files && files.length > 0) {\n        const chars = files\n          .filter((f: any) => f.name.endsWith('.yaml') || f.name.endsWith('.yml'))\n          .map((f: any) => ({\n            id: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n            name: f.name.replace(/\\.ya?ml$/, ''),\n            path: joinPath(charsDir, f.name),\n          }))\n        setCharacterList(chars)\n      } else {\n        setCharacterList([])\n      }\n    } catch {\n      setCharacterList([])\n    } finally {\n      setLoadingCharacters(false)\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (projectRoot) loadCharacters(projectRoot)\n  }, [projectRoot, loadCharacters])\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (currentFile?.content) {\n      const parsed = parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content)\n      setFrontmatter(parsed.frontmatter)\n    } else {\n      setFrontmatter({})\n    }\n  }, [currentFile?.path])\n\n  const handleChapterSelect = useCallback(async (filePath: string) => {\n    if (isDirty) {\n      const confirm = window.confirm('当前章节有未保存的内容，是否保存？')\n      if (confirm) await handleSave()\n    }\n    try {\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.readFile(filePath)\n      if (result.success) {\n        openFile(filePath, result.content || '')\n        setIsDirty(false)\n      }\n    } catch {\n      message.error('读取章节失败')\n    }\n  }, [isDirty, openFile])\n\n  const handleSave = useCallback(async (editorContent?: string) => {\n    if (!currentFile) return\n    setIsSaving(true)\n    try {\n      const contentToSave = editorContent !== undefined\n        ? stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, editorContent)\n        : stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content).content)\n      const result = await window.electronAPI.writeFile(currentFile.path, contentToSave)\n      if (result.success) {\n        openFile(currentFile.path, contentToSave)\n        setIsDirty(false)\n        setLastSaved(new Date())\n        message.success('保存成功')\n      } else {\n        message.error(`保存失败: ${result.error}`)\n      }\n    } catch {\n      message.error('保存文件失败')\n    } finally {\n      setIsSaving(false)\n    }\n  }, [currentFile, frontmatter, openFile])\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (isDirty && currentFile) {\n      if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer)\n      const timer = setTimeout(() => handleSave(), 5000)\n      setAutoSaveTimer(timer)\n    }\n    return () => { if (autoSaveTimer) clearTimeout(autoSaveTimer) }\n  }, [isDirty, currentFile, handleSave])\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handleKeyDown = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      if ((e.ctrlKey || e.metaKey) && e.key === 's') {\n        e.preventDefault()\n        handleSave()\n      }\n    }\n    window.addEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n    return () => window.removeEventListener('keydown', handleKeyDown)\n  }, [handleSave])\n\n  const stats = useMemo(() => {\n    if (!currentFile?.content) return { chinese: 0, total: 0 }\n    const parsed = parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content)\n    return {\n      chinese: countChineseCharacters(parsed.content),\n      total: countTotalCharacters(parsed.content),\n    }\n  }, [currentFile?.content])\n\n  const handleFrontmatterChange = useCallback((newFrontmatter: FrontmatterData) => {\n    setFrontmatter(newFrontmatter)\n    if (currentFile) setIsDirty(true)\n  }, [currentFile])\n\n  const handleOpenProject = useCallback(async () => {\n    const directory = await window.electronAPI.openDirectory()\n    if (directory) {\n      setProjectRoot(directory)\n      message.success(`已打开项目：${directory}`)\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  const handleApplyAIResult = useCallback((content: string) => {\n    if (currentFile) {\n      const newContent = stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, content)\n      openFile(currentFile.path, newContent)\n      setIsDirty(true)\n      setAIOutput('')\n      setStreamingContent('')\n    }\n  }, [currentFile, frontmatter, openFile, setAIOutput, setStreamingContent])\n\n  const siderMenuItems: MenuProps['items'] = [\n    { key: 'outline', icon: <BookOutlined />, label: '大纲导航' },\n    { key: 'characters', icon: <UserOutlined />, label: '角色管理' },\n    { key: 'settings', icon: <SettingOutlined />, label: '世界设定' },\n    { key: 'facts', icon: <ThunderboltOutlined />, label: '事实台账' },\n  ]\n\n  if (!isProjectOpen || !projectRoot) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 48, textAlign: 'center', color: '#888', height: '100vh' }}>\n        <Title level={3}>🍅 创作工作台</Title>\n        <Text>请先打开一个项目</Text>\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  const fileName = currentFile ? currentFile.path.split(/[/\\\\]/).pop() || '' : ''\n  const isMarkdown = fileName.endsWith('.md')\n  const isYaml = fileName.endsWith('.yaml') || fileName.endsWith('.yml')\n  const editorContent = currentFile ? parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content).content : ''\n\n  // 渲染左侧内容\n  const renderLeftContent = () => {\n    if (activeTab === 'outline') {\n      return (\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n          <div style={{ padding: 16, borderBottom: '1px solid #f0f0f0', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n            <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n              <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 8 }}>\n                <UserOutlined />\n                <span style={{ fontWeight: 500 }}>当前视角角色</span>\n              </div>\n              <Select\n                style={{ width: '100%' }}\n                placeholder=\"选择写作视角角色\"\n                loading={loadingCharacters}\n                value={currentCharacter?.id}\n                onChange={(id) => {\n                  if (id) {\n                    const char = characterList.find((c) => c.id === id)\n                    if (char) setCurrentCharacter({ id: char.id, name: char.name, type: 'character', value: char.path })\n                  } else {\n                    setCurrentCharacter(null)\n                  }\n                }}\n                options={characterList.map((c) => ({ label: c.name, value: c.id }))}\n                allowClear\n              />\n            </Space>\n          </div>\n\n          <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto', padding: '0 16px' }}>\n            <RelevantFactsPanel\n              currentPath={projectRoot}\n              currentContent={editorContent}\n              frontmatter={frontmatter}\n              onInsertFact={(content) => {\n                if (!currentFile) return\n                const parsed = parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content)\n                const newContent = stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, parsed.content + content)\n                openFile(currentFile.path, newContent)\n                setIsDirty(true)\n                message.success('已插入设定')\n              }}\n            />\n          </div>\n\n          <Divider style={{ margin: 0 }} />\n\n          <div style={{ padding: '12px 16px 8px', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n            <Title level={5} style={{ margin: 0 }}>📚 大纲导航</Title>\n          </div>\n\n          <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto' }}>\n            <OutlineTree projectRoot={projectRoot} activeChapter={currentFile?.path || null} onSelect={handleChapterSelect} />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'characters') {\n      return <CharacterManager currentPath={projectRoot} onSelectFile={(path) => { openFile(path, ''); setActiveTab('outline') }} />\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'settings') {\n      return <SettingManager currentPath={projectRoot} onSelectFile={(path) => { openFile(path, ''); setActiveTab('outline') }} />\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'facts') {\n      return <FactsPanel />\n    }\n    return null\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100vh', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n      {/* 顶部工具栏 */}\n      <div style={{\n        display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', padding: '0 20px',\n        height: 56, background: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8',\n        justifyContent: 'space-between', flexShrink: 0\n      }}>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 20 }}>\n          <h2 style={{ margin: 0 }}>🍅 创作工作台</h2>\n          <Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 12 }}>{projectRoot}</Text>\n        </div>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 10 }}>\n          <Button icon={<FolderOpenOutlined />} onClick={handleOpenProject}>打开项目</Button>\n          <Button icon={<SaveOutlined />} type=\"primary\" onClick={handleSave} disabled={!isDirty || !currentFile} loading={isSaving}>\n            保存 {isDirty ? '*' : ''}\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* 主体：左侧菜单(64) + 左侧内容(280) + 编辑区(flex) + 右侧AI(360) */}\n      <div style={{ display: 'flex', flex: 1, minHeight: 0, overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n        {/* 左侧图标菜单 */}\n        <div style={{ width: 64, background: '#fff', borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8', flexShrink: 0, overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n          <Menu\n            mode=\"inline\"\n            selectedKeys={[activeTab]}\n            items={siderMenuItems}\n            onClick={({ key }) => setActiveTab(key as TabKey)}\n            style={{ height: '100%', borderRight: 0 }}\n          />\n        </div>\n\n        {/* 左侧内容区 */}\n        <div style={{ width: 280, background: '#fff', borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8', overflow: 'hidden', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n          {renderLeftContent()}\n        </div>\n\n        {/* 中间编辑区 */}\n        <div style={{\n          flex: 1, minWidth: 0, background: '#fff', display: 'flex',\n          flexDirection: 'column', overflow: 'hidden'\n        }}>\n          {currentFile ? (\n            <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', minHeight: 0 }}>\n              {/* 文件标题栏 */}\n              <div style={{\n                padding: '12px 20px', borderBottom: '1px solid #f0f0f0',\n                display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 12, flexShrink: 0\n              }}>\n                <FileTextOutlined />\n                <Text strong style={{ fontSize: 14 }}>{fileName}</Text>\n                <Tag color=\"blue\">{stats.chinese} 汉字</Tag>\n                <Tag color=\"default\">{stats.total} 总字符</Tag>\n                {lastSaved && (\n                  <Space size=\"small\" style={{ marginLeft: 'auto' }}>\n                    <ClockCircleOutlined />\n                    <Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 12 }}>{lastSaved.toLocaleTimeString()}</Text>\n                  </Space>\n                )}\n                {isDirty && <Tag color=\"orange\" style={{ marginLeft: 'auto' }}>未保存</Tag>}\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Frontmatter */}\n              <div style={{ padding: '12px 20px 0', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n                <FrontmatterPanel frontmatter={frontmatter} onChange={handleFrontmatterChange} />\n              </div>\n\n              {/* 编辑器 */}\n              <div style={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0, padding: '0 20px 16px', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n                {isMarkdown && (\n                  <MarkdownEditor content={editorContent} onSave={handleSave} filePath={fileName} />\n                )}\n                {isYaml && (\n                  <YAMLEditor content={currentFile.content} onSave={handleSave} filePath={fileName} />\n                )}\n                {!isMarkdown && !isYaml && (\n                  <textarea\n                    value={editorContent}\n                    onChange={(e) => {\n                      if (currentFile) {\n                        openFile(currentFile.path, stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, e.target.value))\n                        setIsDirty(true)\n                      }\n                    }}\n                    style={{ width: '100%', height: '100%', fontFamily: 'monospace', padding: 16, border: '1px solid #d9d9d9', borderRadius: 4 }}\n                  />\n                )}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <div style={{ display: 'flex', height: '100%', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', color: '#999' }}>\n              <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>\n                <Title level={4}>🍅 创作工作台</Title>\n                <Text type=\"secondary\">从左侧大纲树选择一个文件开始编辑</Text>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        {/* 右侧 AI 工具区 */}\n        <div style={{ width: 360, background: '#fff', borderLeft: '1px solid #e8e8e8', overflow: 'hidden', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n          <div style={{ height: '100%', overflow: 'auto', padding: 16 }}>\n            <WorkspaceAITools currentContent={editorContent} onApplyResult={handleApplyAIResult} />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default IntegratedWorkbench\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43822,"output":4703,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67787,"cost":{"input":0.0131466,"output":0.0056435999999999995,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01994592}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776089123158,"responseId":"062c2b22fa69d87156b7f4ebe44b76b3"}}
