{"type":"message","id":"bff14f2b","parentId":"de08dd1d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:07:05.458Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me build locally and verify it compiles, then sync to Windows. Actually, I should sync the source files and have the user rebuild. But the user builds on Windows with `npm start` which does a full build.\n\nLet me build locally first to verify, then the user can sync (or I can tell them to rebuild).\n\nWait, actually the user is on Windows. The easiest approach is:\n1. Build locally in WSL to verify it compiles\n2. Then the user does `npm start` on Windows which will rebuild\n\nBut the Windows side has the same esbuild issue. The user already fixed it with `npm install esbuild@latest`. So they should be able to build.\n\n\nI'll verify the build in WSL first to catch any TypeScript errors, then the user can rebuild on Windows with `npm start` which will recompile everything including the renderer. For the layout issue, I'm wondering if the problem is actually in the App.tsx case statement rather than the component itself. Looking at the workspace case, it renders `IntegratedWorkbench` with the right props, so that seems fine—but I need to check if there's a case statement issue causing the menu to not display properly when `isProjectOpen` is true.\n\nThe user mentioned \"左边一竖排的功能\" which sounds like they might be seeing the old project view sidebar, not the new workspace menu. So they probably need to manually select the workspace option from the left menu since the component doesn't auto-switch when a project opens. I should ask them to confirm which view they're actually looking at and whether they've selected the workspace option.\n\nActually, wait—looking at that screenshot URL more carefully, the path shows `ccv2/2026-04-13/MiniMax-M2.7/...` which suggests it's from a previous session. The user might have sent an old image. Regardless, the new build should fix the layout issues, so I'll just have them rebuild and check if the workspace renders correctly.","thinkingSignature":"a35d3542acdb8fc2e222088fc71f799137914c77060437e22704c022931ad814"},{"type":"text","text":"彻底换了方案——用**纯 flexbox div** 替代 Ant Design Layout/Sider 组件，彻底规避组件渲染问题。\n\n现在本地 build 验证：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_omom8u680t3n_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app && npm run build 2>&1 | grep -E \"error|ERROR|built|✓\" | head -20","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48573,"output":512,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68347,"cost":{"input":0.014571899999999999,"output":0.0006144,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01634202}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776089207909,"responseId":"062c2b77eb0cd67828f01da9872297c8"}}
