from WSL—the timestamps might not update properly on the Windows side even though the changes are being written.","thinkingSignature":"3d71f7ae8473d15f9302fa1fa4ab79584655ed51c61890cd0632bc2e7d83ed74"},{"type":"text","text":"文件太大了贴不下。既然 WSL 和 Windows 共用同一个 D 盘，Windows 直接打开文件编辑就行了，不需要跨系统复制。\n\n在 **Windows PowerShell** 里直接运行：\n\n```\nnotepad D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\\novel-desktop-app\\src\\renderer\\src\\components\\IntegratedWorkbench.tsx\n```\n\n打开后是旧文件（flexbox 之前的版本），全部删除，复制我上面输出的内容（全选复制），粘贴进去，保存。\n\n然后直接跑 `npm start`（不需要重新 build，prestart 会自动 rebuild）。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":53265,"output":573,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73100,"cost":{"input":0.0159795,"output":0.0006876,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01782282}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776089603618,"responseId":"062c2d03eb4b769794fdd9b16fed2dec"}}
