{"type":"message","id":"39d1e512","parentId":"c015811d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:15:02.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if WSL is on D: drive. No - WSL is a Linux subsystem installed on the Windows machine. The D: drive in Windows corresponds to /mnt/d/ in WSL Ubuntu.\n\nSo WSL Ubuntu is installed on the Windows system drive (usually C:), and /mnt/d/ in WSL is the D: drive on Windows.","thinkingSignature":"b9cc970e07ce27a4221002d399032809a0c14c611265f7c23543826f655647eb"},{"type":"text","text":"不是。WSL 是 Linux 子系统，装在 Windows 的 C 盘里。\n\nWSL 里的 `/mnt/d/` = Windows 的 D 盘。它们共享同一个 D 盘，但 WSL 系统本身在 C 盘。\n\n所以 `\\\\wsl$\\Ubuntu` 指向的是 Windows C 盘上的 WSL 系统目录，不是 D 盘上的文件。\n\n这就是为什么 `\\\\wsl$\\Ubuntu\\mnt\\d\\...` 找不到——`mnt` 不是 WSL 根目录下的文件夹，而是虚拟 Linux 文件系统里的一个挂载点，映射到 Windows 的 D 盘。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54,"output":201,"cacheRead":67899,"cacheWrite":4318,"totalTokens":72472,"cost":{"input":0.0000162,"output":0.00024119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00407394,"cacheWrite":0.00161925,"total":0.0059505899999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776089692319,"responseId":"062c2d5ae57f4b071f0207d4b8764321"}}
