195ms build could be using `vite.simple.config.ts` which might only build the renderer. But if that's the case, why is the user still seeing the old Layout/Sider version? I suspect the file write to `/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/IntegratedWorkbench.tsx` didn't actually persist, or the build isn't picking up the new file correctly.\n\nRather than keep guessing, I should have the user run the build command directly and share the output to see what's actually being compiled.","thinkingSignature":"d711bfc94d0220b9f45617f46ebfa25d8a69f048303073f1b4ac0d86f5eff775"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我深度思考一下，不再盲猜。\n\n你说\"毫无变化\"，Build 输出是 195ms（之前成功的是 88s）。这说明 **Windows 的 build 可能用了缓存或者没有真正重新编译**，只编译了 18 个模块而不是正常的 4218 个。\n\n先在 Windows 上跑这条，看完整输出：\n\n```\ncd D:\\aafuzhi\\axs\\novel-desktop-app\nnpx vite build --config vite.simple.config.ts 2>&1 | findstr /C:\"error\" /C:\"ERROR\" /C:\"built\" /C:\"modules\"\n```\n\n输出是什么？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":659,"cacheRead":79190,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":79849,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0.0007907999999999999,"cacheRead":0.004751399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005542199999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776090892619,"responseId":"062c320a9d08c3b22b717b9cf083a365"}}
