{"type":"message","id":"51771210","parentId":"b9523182","timestamp":"2026-04-13T14:47:59.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The CSS IS in the build output! I can see:\n```css\n.content-panel{border-radius:8px;height:calc(100vh - 120px);overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 1px 4px #0000000f;display:flex;flex-direction:column}\n```\n\nSo the CSS change is there. `display:flex` and `flex-direction:column` are in the minified CSS.\n\nBut the user says there's NO CHANGE. The `.content-panel` CSS now has `display:flex`. But my `IntegratedWorkbench` root element is a plain `<div>` with `display: flex; flex-direction: column; height: 100vh; overflow: hidden`.\n \nAh, I see the issue now. The `IntegratedWorkbench` has `height: 100vh` set directly, but inside the `.content-panel` container with `display: flex; flex-direction: column`, that `100vh` height would actually be constrained by the parent's dimensions. The 100vh on the child isn't doing what I expected because flexbox is controlling the layout from the parent level.\n\nLet me trace through the actual DOM structure from App.tsx to understand what's happening with the Sider components and their positioning.\n\nLooking at the user's report that only the left sidebar shows, it seems like the `IntegratedWorkbench` component is rendering but not expanding properly within the `.content-panel` flex container. The Sider width of 64 is there, but the rest of the content isn't visible—suggesting either the flex child isn't growing to fill available space, or there's a rendering issue with how the Layout component is being parsed.\n\nThe minified CSS output might be getting corrupted somewhere in the build or copy process, or perhaps there's a Vite cache issue preventing the updated styles from taking effect. Let me verify whether the built JavaScript bundle actually contains the flexbox layout code I wrote.","thinkingSignature":"c14bc678d99c782732862d1e336e428fce2680449a78d638d493af63963b0a6b"},{"type":"text","text":"CSS 修改已经打进去了（`.content-panel{border-radius:8px;...display:flex;flex-direction:column}`）。但你说还是没变化。\n\n让我验证 JS 里的布局代码：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pgsktu38bzze_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -o \"display.*flex.*flexDirection.*column\\|创作工作台\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/dist/renderer/assets/index-*.js 2>/dev/null | head -3"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pgsktu38bzze_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -c \"IntegratedWorkbench\" /mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/dist/renderer/assets/index-*.js 2>/dev/null"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65756,"output":559,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85577,"cost":{"input":0.0197268,"output":0.0006707999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.021553319999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776091661493,"responseId":"062c350c81620fe98dd65b3277ae139c"}}
