{"type":"message","id":"4cfe3490","parentId":"afa887e6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T15:26:01.942Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see another issue - `handleChapterSelect` depends on `isDirty` but `isDirty` is a local state, not a store. This should be fine since it's in the dependency array.\n\nHowever, I notice that `handleSave` is in the dependency array of `useEffect` for auto-save, but `handleSave` changes when `currentFile` or `frontmatter` or `openFile` changes. This could cause the auto-save timer to be reset frequently.\n\nBut more importantly, let me look at the actual issues:1. `handleChapterSelect` depends on `isDirty` - but this is fine since `isDirty` is a state variable","thinkingSignature":"c5674756c8a75da62d98b077b91b05ea9877b2ea26c33187a3fb1504cbd125ae"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gvqc6mwfb9jp_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/IntegratedWorkbench.tsx","offset":171,"limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92071,"output":211,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111544,"cost":{"input":0.027621299999999998,"output":0.0002532,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029030219999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776093955530,"responseId":"062c3e02713b0018e798e5445840f7cd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"91a85c0e","parentId":"4cfe3490","timestamp":"2026-04-13T15:26:02.034Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gvqc6mwfb9jp_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return {\n      chinese: countChineseCharacters(parsed.content),\n      total: countTotalCharacters(parsed.content),\n    }\n  }, [currentFile?.content])\n\n  const handleFrontmatterChange = useCallback((newFrontmatter: FrontmatterData) => {\n    setFrontmatter(newFrontmatter)\n    if (currentFile) setIsDirty(true)\n  }, [currentFile])\n\n  const handleOpenProject = useCallback(async () => {\n    const directory = await window.electronAPI.openDirectory()\n    if (directory) {\n      setProjectRoot(directory)\n      message.success(`已打开项目：${directory}`)\n    }\n  }, [])\n\n  const handleApplyAIResult = useCallback((content: string) => {\n    if (currentFile) {\n      const newContent = stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, content)\n      openFile(currentFile.path, newContent)\n      setIsDirty(true)\n      setAIOutput('')\n      setStreamingContent('')\n    }\n  }, [currentFile, frontmatter, openFile, setAIOutput, setStreamingContent])\n\n  const siderMenuItems: MenuProps['items'] = [\n    { key: 'outline', icon: <BookOutlined />, label: '大纲导航' },\n    { key: 'characters', icon: <UserOutlined />, label: '角色管理' },\n    { key: 'settings', icon: <SettingOutlined />, label: '世界设定' },\n    { key: 'facts', icon: <ThunderboltOutlined />, label: '事实台账' },\n  ]\n\n  if (!isProjectOpen || !projectRoot) {\n    return (\n      <div style={{ padding: 48, textAlign: 'center', color: '#888', height: '100vh' }}>\n        <Title level={3}>🍅 创作工作台</Title>\n        <Text>请先打开一个项目</Text>\n      </div>\n    )\n  }\n\n  const fileName = currentFile ? currentFile.path.split(/[/\\\\]/).pop() || '' : ''\n  const isMarkdown = fileName.endsWith('.md')\n  const isYaml = fileName.endsWith('.yaml') || fileName.endsWith('.yml')\n  const editorContent = currentFile ? parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content).content : ''\n\n  const renderLeftContent = () => {\n    if (activeTab === 'outline') {\n      return (\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n          <div style={{ padding: 16, borderBottom: '1px solid #f0f0f0', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n            <Space direction=\"vertical\" style={{ width: '100%' }}>\n              <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 8 }}>\n                <UserOutlined />\n                <span style={{ fontWeight: 500 }}>当前视角角色</span>\n              </div>\n              <Select\n                style={{ width: '100%' }}\n                placeholder=\"选择写作视角角色\"\n                loading={loadingCharacters}\n                value={currentCharacter?.id}\n                onChange={(id) => {\n                  if (id) {\n                    const char = characterList.find((c) => c.id === id)\n                    if (char) setCurrentCharacter({ id: char.id, name: char.name, type: 'character', value: char.path })\n                  } else {\n                    setCurrentCharacter(null)\n                  }\n                }}\n                options={characterList.map((c) => ({ label: c.name, value: c.id }))}\n                allowClear\n              />\n            </Space>\n          </div>\n\n          <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto', padding: '0 16px' }}>\n\n[140 more lines in file. Use offset=251 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776093962021}}
{"type":"message","id":"b84cd00d","parentId":"91a85c0e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T15:26:09.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see an important issue! The `renderLeftContent` function is a regular function (not memoized), which means it gets recreated on every render. Inside it references `activeTab`, `projectRoot`, `characterList`, `currentCharacter`, `editorContent`, `frontmatter`, etc. But since it's an arrow function defined inside the component body, it has access to the latest values through closure.\n\nActually, this is fine in React - it's just a function, not a performance issue unless we're passing it as a prop to memoized children.\n\nBut there IS a significant issue: the `renderLeftContent` function is defined inside the component body, which means it's recreated on every render. This is not ideal but not a bug.\n\n\nLet me keep reviewing the rest of the component.","thinkingSignature":"38a12ce2a7d87c482c2d2a410d367b20bf99a1557af236f414a23bd5aa32b01d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_e04n0ltn0b6p_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/mnt/d/aafuzhi/axs/novel-desktop-app/src/renderer/src/components/IntegratedWorkbench.tsx","offset":251,"limit":140}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93104,"output":229,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112595,"cost":{"input":0.0279312,"output":0.0002748,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029361719999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776093962037,"responseId":"062c3e0980c232c3b012707071767c4a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c1b4e662","parentId":"b84cd00d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T15:26:09.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_e04n0ltn0b6p_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            <RelevantFactsPanel\n              currentPath={projectRoot}\n              currentContent={editorContent}\n              frontmatter={frontmatter}\n              onInsertFact={(content) => {\n                if (!currentFile) return\n                const parsed = parseFrontmatter(currentFile.content)\n                const newContent = stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, parsed.content + content)\n                openFile(currentFile.path, newContent)\n                setIsDirty(true)\n                message.success('已插入设定')\n              }}\n            />\n          </div>\n\n          <Divider style={{ margin: 0 }} />\n\n          <div style={{ padding: '12px 16px 8px', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n            <Title level={5} style={{ margin: 0 }}>📚 大纲导航</Title>\n          </div>\n\n          <div style={{ flex: 1, overflow: 'auto' }}>\n            <OutlineTree projectRoot={projectRoot} activeChapter={currentFile?.path || null} onSelect={handleChapterSelect} />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'characters') {\n      return <CharacterManager currentPath={projectRoot} onSelectFile={(path) => { openFile(joinPath(projectRoot!, path), ''); setActiveTab('outline') }} />\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'settings') {\n      return <SettingManager currentPath={projectRoot} onSelectFile={(path) => { openFile(joinPath(projectRoot!, path), ''); setActiveTab('outline') }} />\n    }\n    if (activeTab === 'facts') {\n      return <FactsPanel />\n    }\n    return null\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100vh', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n      <div style={{\n        display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', padding: '0 20px',\n        height: 56, background: '#fff', borderBottom: '1px solid #e8e8e8',\n        justifyContent: 'space-between', flexShrink: 0\n      }}>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 20 }}>\n          <h2 style={{ margin: 0 }}>🍅 创作工作台</h2>\n          <Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 12 }}>{projectRoot}</Text>\n        </div>\n        <div style={{ display: 'flex', gap: 10 }}>\n          <Button icon={<FolderOpenOutlined />} onClick={handleOpenProject}>打开项目</Button>\n          <Button icon={<SaveOutlined />} type=\"primary\" onClick={handleSave} disabled={!isDirty || !currentFile} loading={isSaving}>\n            保存 {isDirty ? '*' : ''}\n          </Button>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div style={{ display: 'flex', flex: 1, minHeight: 0, overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n        <div style={{ width: 64, background: '#fff', borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8', flexShrink: 0, overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n          <Menu\n            mode=\"inline\"\n            selectedKeys={[activeTab]}\n            items={siderMenuItems}\n            onClick={({ key }) => setActiveTab(key as TabKey)}\n            style={{ height: '100%', borderRight: 0 }}\n          />\n        </div>\n\n        <div style={{ width: 280, background: '#fff', borderRight: '1px solid #e8e8e8', overflow: 'hidden', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n          {renderLeftContent()}\n        </div>\n\n        <div style={{ flex: 1, minWidth: 0, background: '#fff', display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n          {currentFile ? (\n            <div style={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', height: '100%', minHeight: 0 }}>\n              <div style={{\n                padding: '12px 20px', borderBottom: '1px solid #f0f0f0',\n                display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: 12, flexShrink: 0\n              }}>\n                <FileTextOutlined />\n                <Text strong style={{ fontSize: 14 }}>{fileName}</Text>\n                <Tag color=\"blue\">{stats.chinese} 汉字</Tag>\n                <Tag color=\"default\">{stats.total} 总字符</Tag>\n                {lastSaved && (\n                  <Space size=\"small\" style={{ marginLeft: 'auto' }}>\n                    <ClockCircleOutlined />\n                    <Text type=\"secondary\" style={{ fontSize: 12 }}>{lastSaved.toLocaleTimeString()}</Text>\n                  </Space>\n                )}\n                {isDirty && <Tag color=\"orange\" style={{ marginLeft: 'auto' }}>未保存</Tag>}\n              </div>\n\n              <div style={{ padding: '12px 20px 0', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n                <FrontmatterPanel frontmatter={frontmatter} onChange={handleFrontmatterChange} />\n              </div>\n\n              <div style={{ flex: 1, minHeight: 0, padding: '0 20px 16px', overflow: 'hidden' }}>\n                {isMarkdown && (\n                  <MarkdownEditor content={editorContent} onSave={handleSave} filePath={fileName} />\n                )}\n                {isYaml && (\n                  <YAMLEditor content={currentFile.content} onSave={handleSave} filePath={fileName} />\n                )}\n                {!isMarkdown && !isYaml && (\n                  <textarea\n                    value={editorContent}\n                    onChange={(e) => {\n                      if (currentFile) {\n                        openFile(currentFile.path, stringifyFrontmatter(frontmatter, e.target.value))\n                        setIsDirty(true)\n                      }\n                    }}\n                    style={{ width: '100%', height: '100%', fontFamily: 'monospace', padding: 16, border: '1px solid #d9d9d9', borderRadius: 4 }}\n                  />\n                )}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          ) : (\n            <div style={{ display: 'flex', height: '100%', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', color: '#999' }}>\n              <div style={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>\n                <Title level={4}>🍅 创作工作台</Title>\n                <Text type=\"secondary\">从左侧大纲树选择一个文件开始编辑</Text>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          )}\n        </div>\n\n        <div style={{ width: 360, background: '#fff', borderLeft: '1px solid #e8e8e8', overflow: 'hidden', flexShrink: 0 }}>\n          <div style={{ height: '100%', overflow: 'auto', padding: 16 }}>\n            <WorkspaceAITools currentContent={editorContent} onApplyResult={handleApplyAIResult} />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n\nexport default IntegratedWorkbench\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776093969814}}
{"type":"message","id":"db957124","parentId":"c1b4e662","timestamp":"2026-04-13T15:26:35.379Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me review the complete code. I see several issues:\n\n### Critical Issues\n\n1. **`RelevantFactsPanel` receives `currentContent` prop but it only reads `editorContent` once at render time** - when the file changes, the panel won't refresh its relevance scores because `currentContent` is just passed as a value, not as a ref that's tracked. But this is not a crash issue, just a stale data issue.\n\n2. **`renderLeftContent` is not memoized** - it's an inline function defined in the render body, which means it's recreated on every render. This causes all child components inside it to potentially re-render. Not a bug but a performance issue.\n   \n3. **`handleOpenProject` only updates the project root but never triggers a file tree reload**, so the outline won't refresh after switching projects.\n\n4. **No cleanup for `window.electronAPI.fsWatch` listeners** - the effect in `OutlineTree` sets up a watcher but there's no mechanism to remove it when the component unmounts, which could cause memory leaks.\n\n5. **ESLint would flag missing dependencies** - the effect hooks have incomplete dependency arrays that would trigger warnings about `handleSave` not being included where it should be.","thinkingSignature":"ff8dfbfc27ea3d4d873b449685db1af4b1be052c178d71026c91d6e872c07df0"},{"type":"text","text":"## 代码审查结果\n\n### 🔴 严重问题（可能导致运行时崩溃）\n\n**无。** 主要逻辑完整。\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 功能/逻辑问题\n\n| # | 问题 | 位置 | 影响 |\n|---|------|------|------|\n| 1 | `handleChapterSelect` 依赖 `isDirty` 但缺少 `handleSave` 在 dep array | L113 | 保存确认弹窗无法正常工作 |\n| 2 | `loadCharacters` 的 `useEffect` 没有处理 `plots` 目录不存在的情况 | L88-89 | 首次打开项目时 characters_facts.yaml 不存在会静默失败 |\n| 3 | `openFile(path, '')` 空内容后没有触发 `loadFile` | L279,282 | 打开文件时内容为空，需要再次触发读取 |\n| 4 | `handleOpenProject` 成功后没有重置 `isDirty` 和 `frontmatter` 状态 | L184-188 | 切换项目后旧状态残留 |\n\n---\n\n### 🟠 性能/代码质量\n\n| # | 问题 | 位置 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | `renderLeftContent` 是普通函数未 memo，每次 render 都重建 | L213 |\n| 2 | `activeTab` 变化时整个左侧内容区全部重新渲染 | - |\n| 3 | auto-save `useEffect` 依赖 `handleSave`，导致 timer 频繁重置 | L148-155 |\n| 4 | `window.electronAPI` 无类型定义，任何拼写错误都是运行时才发现 | 全局 |\n\n---\n\n### 🟢 已正确处理\n\n- ✅ `joinPath` 替换 Node.js `path` — Vite 兼容\n- ✅ `../../../renderer/index.html` 路径 — 三层正确\n- ✅ `App.css content-panel display:flex` — flex 布局生效\n- ✅ CharacterManager/SettingManager `onSelectFile` 拼接 `joinPath(projectRoot, path)`\n- ✅ `handleSave` 参数 `editorContent?: string` — 兼容 MarkdownEditor 接口\n- ✅ frontmatter 和 editor 状态分离管理\n\n---\n\n**最关键的 Bug 修复建议：** `handleChapterSelect` 的 `useCallback` 缺少 `handleSave` 在 dep array，以及 `onSelectFile` 后应立即读取文件内容。\n\n要我修这些问题吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94888,"output":745,"cacheRead":19262,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114895,"cost":{"input":0.0284664,"output":0.0008939999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0011557199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030516119999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776093969830,"responseId":"062c3e10c9ead50779d24bbcbc5c9a5f"}}
